series_description:
This series documents facilities, services
and other accommodations provided by
the institution for events on campus.
Records may include: facilities reservation
agreements; room reservation lists;
customer and room occupancy lists;
catering service orders; purchase and
supply records; customer evaluations;
summary report; and related
correspondence.

